Description: Tsukune Aono’s new school is filled with vampires and werewolves. And the girl he is interested seems to have eyes for him, but is it his blood she’s after?
Title: ROSARIO   VAMPIRE: SEASON II, VOL. 1
Author: Akihisa Ikeda

Description: Naruto learns more secrets from his past and moves closer to discovering the identity of his nemesis, Pain.
Title: NARUTO, VOL. 47
Author: Masashi Kishimoto

Description: A star-crossed romance set at a private academy begins in the past when, in return for a loan of 50 million yen, the prestigious Kamiya family gave their daughter Haine away to the Otomiya family.
Title: THE GENTLEMEN’S ALLIANCE, VOL.11
Author: Arina Tanemura

Description: Resurrection day looms when the evil Yako Tenma takens over the gaming company Kaibacorp and its technology to bring the dead back to life.
Title: YU-GI-OH! R, VOL. 4
Author: Kazuki Takahashi and Akira Ito
Contributor: by Kazuki Takahashi and Akira Ito

Description: In this dark future, the required elements for survival are sword, gun, courage and luck.
Title: DOGS, VOL. 3
Author: Shirow Miwa

Description: Sebastian is a loyal butler who moves easily from dinner parties to the underworld. Is he too good to be true? Is he even human?
Title: BLACK BUTLER, VOL. 1
Author: Yana Toboso

Description: Kagome, a modern day girl finds herself in Japan’s ancient past. This chapter has tragic consequences.
Title: INUYASHA, VOL. 47
Author: Rumiko Takahashi

Description: Cross Academy has day and evening students, but the latter have a secret: they are vampires.
Title: VAMPIRE KNIGHT, VOL. 9
Author: Matsuri Hino

Description: Maka, an arms expert, wants to turn the Soul Eater, her living scythe, into the ultimate weapon for Death.
Title: SOUL EATER, VOL. 2
Author: Atsushi Ohkubo

Description: Ichigo Kurosaki sees dead people and must help usher them safely into the afterlife.
Title: BLEACH, VOL. 30
Author: Tite Kubo
